i\u0107 wzrost sprzeda\u017cy i dostosowa\u0107 strategi\u0119 w razie potrzeby.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Zastosowanie tej strategii mo\u017ce znacz\u0105co zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c przy minimalnym wysi\u0142ku, zw\u0142aszcza w przypadkach, gdy konta nie w pe\u0142ni wykorzystuj\u0105 swoje mo\u017cliwo\u015bci PPC. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce kluczowe jest ci\u0105g\u0142e monitorowanie wynik\u00f3w i dostosowywanie dzia\u0142a\u0144.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c dzi\u0119ki strategii PPC?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak poprawi\u0107 wyniki sp<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7828,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7827","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-marketplace"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7827"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7827"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7827\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7828"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7827"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7827"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/w